high_descs: turn left and walk to the bath tub at the end of the room
pick up the dirty wash cloth out of the bath tub
turn right and walk over to the sink up ahead on the right
rinse the cloth off in the sink, then take it back out
turn right and walk back over to the bath tub on the right
place the cloth back in the tub
anns.task_desc: place a clean cloth inside the bath tub

high_descs: pick up dirty red rag from tub
turn around, go to sink to the left
place red rag in sink, turn on water, turn off water, pick up red rag from sink
place clean red rag in bathtub to the left of green sponge in bathtub
anns.task_desc: Place clean red rag in bathtub

high_descs: Turn around and then move straight to the bath tub.
Pick up the cloth from the bath tub.
Hold the cloth and turn around. Face the sink on the left side.
Place the cloth in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the cloth.
Carry the cloth and turn to the right. Face the tub on the right side.
Place the cloth in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Clean a cloth and place it in the bath tub.
